Preparations
============

Install "Google Data APIs Python Client Library" from here: http://code.google.com/p/gdata-python-client/ (or possibly from sudo apt-get install python-gdata)

Install perl markdown (the original markdown engine)
sudo apt-get install markdown


Usage
=====

Run ./auth.py to get ./token, which will hold an authentication token.

Run ./list.py to list out your blogs. Choose a blog_id (the number) and store it in ./blog_id

Run ./add.py to add all blog posts to the blogger blog.
